<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑数调减法，是指在乘数的某位数上，适当凑上一些数，使其成为同数，然后按“同数错位法”运算，最后，再减去所凑之数与被乘数之积的一种求积方法，。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">10ma+ma-bm</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中m为被乘数，a为同数（挂数）的某一位数字，b为乘数所凑的数。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">92×53=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 92×53</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=10×92×5+92×5-2×92</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4600+460-184</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4876</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>